Name: Suspicious Mountains, Sea, and Sky
Desc: A large platter with a mix of meat and vegetables. First, you find yourself biting into a half-rare skewer of meat; second, a chunk of charred fish. The contrast is so jarring that you simply can't muster up the courage to take a third bite...
Effect: Decreases all party members' gliding and sprinting Stamina consumption by 15% for 900s. In Co-Op Mode, this effect only applies to your own character(s).
